	<input type="text" name="tsearch" id="desktopSearch">
	<section class="result-data"></section>
	<script>
		(function($){
			$(document).ready(function(){
			    let csrf_name   = [$('input[name="csrf_token"]').attr('name')];
			    let csrf_hash   = $('input[name="csrf_token"]').val();
			    let currentPage = 1;
			    let perPage     = 15;
			    let searchQuery = '';
			    let sortColumn  = '';
			    let sortOrder   = 'asc';
			    let startDate   = '';
			    let endDate     = '';

			    function loadEmployeeData() {
			        let req;
			        req = $.ajax({
			            url: "/customer/read",
			            type: 'POST',
			            data: {
			                csrf_name: csrf_hash,
			                search: searchQuery,
			                column: sortColumn,
			                order: sortOrder,
			                perpage: perPage,
			                page: currentPage,
			                start_date: startDate,
			                end_date: endDate
			            },
			            dataType: 'json',
			            cache: false,
			        });
			        req.done(response =>{
			            let $data = response;
			            $('.result-data').html($data.results);
			            $('.pagination').html($data.pager);
			         });
			         req.fail(()=>{
			           alert("Error: check your internet connection.");         
			         });
			    }

				function actionEmployee()
				{
				    // Search keyup event
				    $(document).on('keyup','#desktopSearch, #mobileSearch', function() {
				        searchQuery = $(this).val();
				        currentPage = 1;
				        loadEmployeeData();
				    });
				    
				    // Pagination click event
				    $(document).on('click touch', 'ul.pagination li a', function(e) {
				        e.preventDefault();
				        currentPage = $(this).data('page');
				        loadEmployeeData();
				    });
				}   

			    actionEmployee();
			    loadEmployeeData();
			     
			});	
		})(jQuery);
	</script>
